   plain:'30% of semen volume. Contains PSA (prostate-specific antigen), zinc, citric acid, enzymes. Smooth muscle contracts during orgasm to propel semen. Grows throughout life — benign enlargement affects 50% of men by age 60. Prostate cancer: most common cancer in men.',
